OL,3,CPolice probe after dozens of frogs
OL,4,C'deliberately' killed
OL,6,FPolice say they are investigating a
OL,7,F"disturbing" attack during which
OL,8,Fdozens of frogs were dismembered at a
OL,9,Fpond in Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FAround 50 amphibians were
OL,12,F"deliberately" killed at the pond in a
OL,13,Fresidential area of Grantham overnight
OL,14,Fon Thursday.
OL,16,FThe frogs appeared to have been killed
OL,17,Fwith a garden strimmer or a similar
OL,18,Ftool, Lincolnshire Police said, adding
OL,19,Fthat "a significant amount of
OL,20,Ffrogspawn" had also been removed from
OL,21,Fthe pond.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
