FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1773083488
OL,3,CPolice probe after dozens of frogs
OL,4,C'deliberately' killed
OL,6,FIn a post issued by the force's Rural
OL,7,FCrime Action Team, a police
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Between 3pm on
OL,9,FThursday 6 March and the morning of
OL,10,FFriday 7 March, it is believed that
OL,11,Fapproximately 50 frogs and toads were
OL,12,Fdeliberately killed, and a significant
OL,13,Famount of frogspawn, both clear and
OL,14,Fblack, was removed from the pond.
OL,16,F"They appear to have been cut into
OL,17,Fpieces, possibly using a strimmer or
OL,18,Fsimilar garden tool."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1773083488
OL,3,CPolice probe after dozens of frogs
OL,4,C'deliberately' killed
OL,6,FThey added: "We are keen to speak with
OL,7,Fanyone who was in the area during this
OL,8,Ftime, or who may have seen or heard
OL,9,Fsomeone using gardening equipment near
OL,10,Fa pond, or noticed any suspicious
OL,11,Fbehaviour."
OL,13,FLocal councillor Chris Harrowby said
OL,14,Fhe was "appalled" by the sight of the
OL,15,Fdead amphibians.
OL,17,FAnyone with information on the
OL,18,Fincident is being urged to contact
OL,19,FLincolnshire Police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
